quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  35,1,EL-HEMDU LILLAHI FATIRI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI XHA’ILIL-MELA’IKETI RUSULÆN ‘ULI ‘EXHNIHETIN METHNA WE THULATHE WE RUBA’A JEZIDU FIL-HALKI MA JESHA’U ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  35,2,MA JEFTEHI ELLAHU LILNNASI MIN REHMETIN FELA MUMSIKE LEHA WE MA JUMSIK FELA MURSILE LEHU MIN BA’DIHI WE HUWEL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  35,3,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU EDHKURU NI’METEL-LAHI ‘ALEJKUM HEL MIN HALIKIN GAJRU ELLAHI JERZUKUKUM MINE ES-SEMA’I WEL-’ERDI LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE FE’ENNA TU’UFEKUNE
  35,4,WE ‘IN JUKEDHDHIBUKE FEKAD KUDHDHIBET RUSULUN MIN KABLIKE WE ‘ILA ELLAHI TURXHA’UL-’UMURU
  35,5,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU ‘INNE WA’DEL-LAHI HEKKUN FELA TEGURRENNEKUMUL-HEJA ETU ED-DUNJA WE LA JEGURRENNEKUM BILLAHIL-GARURU
  35,6,‘INNE ESH-SHEJTANE LEKUM ‘ADUWUN FE ETTEHIDHUHU ‘ADUWÆN ‘INNEMA JED’U HIZBEHU LIJEKUNU MIN ‘ESHABI ES-SA’IRI
  35,7,EL-LEDHINE KEFERU LEHUM ‘ADHABUN SHEDIDUN WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI LEHUM MEGFIRETUN WE ‘EXHRUN KEBIRUN
  35,8,‘EFEMEN ZUJJINE LEHU SU’U ‘AMELIHI FERE’AHU HESENÆN FE’INNALL-LLAHE JUDILLU MEN JESHA’U WE JEHDI MEN JESHA’U FELA TEDH/HEB NEFSUKE ‘ALEJHIM HESERATIN ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALIMUN BIMA JESNA’UNE
  35,9,WEL-LAHUL-LEDHI ‘ERSELE ER-RIJAHE FETUTHIRU SEHABÆN FESUKNAHU ‘ILA BELEDIN MEJJITIN FE’EHJEJNA BIHIL-’ERDE BA’DE MEWTIHA KEDHALIKE EN-NUSHURU
  35,10,MEN KANE JURIDUL-’IZZETE FELILLAHIL-’IZZETU XHEMI’ÆN ‘ILEJHI JES’ADUL-KELIMUT-TEJJIBU WEL-’AMELU ES-SALIHU JERFA’UHU WEL-LEDHINE JEMKURUNE ES-SEJJI’ATI LEHUM ‘ADHABUN SHEDIDUN WE MEKRU ‘ULA’IKE HUWE JEBURU
  35,11,WEL-LAHU HALEKAKUM MIN TURABIN THUMME MIN NUTFETIN THUMME XHE’ALEKUM ‘EZWAXHÆN WE MA TEHMILU MIN ‘UNTHA WE LA TEDA’U ‘ILLA BI’ILMIHI WE MA JU’AMMERU MIN MU’AMMERIN WE LA JUNKASU MIN ‘UMURIHI ‘ILLA FI KITABIN ‘INNE DHALIKE ‘ALA ELLAHI JESIRUN
  35,12,WE MA JESTEWIL-BEHRANI HADHA ‘ADHBUN FURATUN SA’IGUN SHERABUHU WE HEDHA MILHUN ‘UXHAXHUN WE MIN KULLIN TE’KULUNE LEHMÆN TERIJÆN WE TESTEHRIXHUNE HILJETEN TELBESUNEHA WE TERAL-FULKE FIHI MEWAHIRE LITEBTEGU MIN FEDLIHI WE LE’ALLEKUM TESHKURUNE
  35,13,JULIXHUL-LEJLE FI EN-NEHARI WE JULIXHU EN-NEHARE FIL-LEJLI WE SEHHARE ESH-SHEMSE WEL-KAMERE KULLUN JEXHRI LI’XHELIN MUSEMMEN DHELIKUMU ELLAHU REBBUKUM LEHUL-MULKU WEL-LEDHINE TED’UNE MIN DUNIHI MA JEMLIKUNE MIN KITMIRIN
  35,14,‘IN TED’UHUM LA JESMA’U DU’A’EKUM WE LEW SEMI’U MA ESTEXHABU LEKUM WE JEWMEL-KIJAMETI JEKFURUNE BISHIRKIKUM WE LA JUNEBBI’UKE MITHLU HABIRIN
  35,15,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU ‘ENTUMUL-FUKARA’U ‘ILA ELLAHI WEL-LAHU HUWEL-GANIJUL-HEMIDU
  35,16,‘IN JESHE’ JUDH/HIBKUM WE JE’TI BIHALKIN XHEDIDIN
  35,17,WE MA DHALIKE ‘ALA ELLAHI BI’AZIZIN
  35,18,WE LA TEZIRU WAZIRETUN WIZRE ‘UHRA WE ‘IN TED’U MUTHKALETUN ‘ILA HIMLIHA LA JUHMEL MINHU SHEJ’UN WE LEW KANE DHA KURBA ‘INNEMA TUNDHIRUL-LEDHINE JEHSHEWNE REBBEHUM BIL-GAJBI WE ‘EKAMU ES-SELÆTE WE MEN TEZEKKA FE’INNEMA JETEZEKKA LINEFSIHI WE ‘ILA ELLAHIL
  35,19,WE MA JESTEWIL-’A’MA WEL-BESIRU
  35,20,WE LA EDH-DHULUMATU WE LA EN-NUR
  35,21,WE LA EDH-DHILLU WE LAL-HERURU
  35,22,WE MA JESTEWIL-’EHJA’U WE LAL-’EMWATU ‘INNALL-LLAHE JUSMI’U MEN JESHA’U WE MA ‘ENTE BIMUSMI’IN MEN FIL-KUBURI
  35,23,‘IN ‘ENTE ‘ILLA NEDHIRUN
  35,24,‘INNA ‘ERSELNAKE BIL-HEKKI BESHIRÆN WE NEDHIRÆN WE ‘IN MIN ‘UMMETIN ‘ILLA HALA FIHA NEDHIRUN
  35,25,WE ‘IN JUKEDHDHIBUKE FEKAD KEDHDHEBEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM XHA’ET/HUM RUSULUHUM BIL-BEJJINATI WE BIZ-ZUBURI WE BIL-KITABIL-MUNIRI
  35,26,THUMME ‘EHADHTUL-LEDHINE KEFERU FEKEJFE KANE NEKIRI
  35,27,‘ELEM TERA ‘ENNEL-LAHE ‘ENZELE MINE ES-SEMA’I MA’EN FE’EHREXHNA BIHI THEMERATIN MUHTELIFÆN ‘ELWANUHA WE MINEL-XHIBALI XHUDEDUN BIDUN WE HUMRUN MUHTELIFUN ‘ELWANUHA WE GARABIBU SUDUN
  35,28,WE MINE EN-NASI WE ED-DEWABBI WEL-’EN’AM MUHTELIFUN ‘ELWANUHU KEDHALIKE ‘INNEMA JEHSHA ELLAHE MIN ‘IBADIHIL-’ULEMA’U ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘AZIZUN GAFURUN
  35,29,‘INNEL-LEDHINE JETLUNE KITABEL-LAHI WE ‘EKAMU ES-SELÆTE WE ‘ENFEKU MIMMA REZEKNAHUM SIRRÆN WE ‘ALANIJETEN JERXHUNE TIXHARETEN LEN TEBURE
  35,30,LIJUWEFFIJEHUM ‘UXHUREHUM WE JEZIDEHUM MIN FEDLIHI ‘INNEHU GAFURUN SHEKURUN
  35,31,WEL-LEDHI ‘EWHEJNA ‘ILEJKE MINEL-KITABI HUWEL-HEKKU MUSEDDIKÆN LIMA BEJNE JEDEJHI ‘INNALL-LLAHE BI’IBADIHI LEHABIRUN BESIRUN
  35,32,THUMME ‘EWRETHNAL-KITABEL-LEDHINE ESTEFEJNA MIN ‘IBADINA FEMINHUM DHALIMUN LINEFSIHI WE MINHUM MUKTESIDUN WE MINHUM SABIKUN BIL-HAJRATI BI’IDHNI ELLAHI DHALIKE HUWEL-FEDLUL-KEBIRU
  35,33,XHENNATU ‘ADNIN JEDHULUNEHA JUHELLEWNE FIHA MIN ‘ESAWIRE MIN DHEHEBIN WE LU’ULU’UÆN WE LIBASUHUM FIHA HERIRUN
  35,34,WE KALUL-HEMDU LILLAHIL-LEDHI ‘EDH/HEBE ‘ANNAL-HEZENE ‘INNE REBBENA LEGAFURUN SHEKURUN
  35,35,EL-LEDHI ‘EHELLENA DAREL-MUKAMETI MIN FEDLIHI LA JEMESSUNA FIHA NESEBUN WE LA JEMESSUNA FIHA LUGUBUN
  35,36,WEL-LEDHINE KEFERU LEHUM NARU XHEHENNEME LA JUKDA ‘ALEJHIM FEJEMUTU WE LA JUHAFFEFU ‘ANHUM MIN ‘ADHABIHA KEDHALIKE NEXHZI KULLE KEFURIN
  35,37,WE HUM JESTERIHUNE FIHA REBBENA ‘EHRIXHNA NA’MEL SALIHÆN GAJREL-LEDHI KUNNA NA’MELU ‘EWELEM NU’AMMIRKUM MA JETEDHEKKERU FIHI MEN TEDHEKKERE WE XHA’EKUMU EN-NEDHIRU FEDHUKU FEMA LILDHDHALIMINE MIN NESIR
  35,38,‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALIMU GAJBI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI ‘INNEHU ‘ALIMUN BIDHATI ES-SUDURI
  35,39,HUWEL-LEDHI XHE’ALEKUM HALA’IFE FIL-’ERDI FEMEN KEFERE FE’ALEJHI KUFRUHU WE LA JEZIDUL-KAFIRINE KUFRUHUM ‘INDE RABBIHIM ‘ILLA MEKTÆN WE LA JEZIDUL-KAFIRINE KUFRUHUM ‘ILLA HASARÆN
  35,40,KUL ‘ERE’EJTUM SHUREKA’EKUMUL-LEDHINE TED’UNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI ‘ERUNI MADHA HALEKU MINEL-’ERDI ‘EM LEHUM SHIRKUN FI ES-SEMAWATI ‘EM ‘ATEJNAHUM KITABÆN FEHUM ‘ALA BEJJINETIN MINHU BEL ‘IN JA’IDU EDH-DHALIMUNE BA’DUHUM BA’DÆN ‘ILLA GURURÆN
  35,41,‘INNALL-LLAHE JUMSIKU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE ‘EN TEZULA WE LE’IN ZALETA ‘IN ‘EMSEKEHUMA MIN ‘EHEDIN MIN BA’DIHI ‘INNEHU KANE HELIMÆN GAFURÆN
  35,42,WE ‘EKSEMU BILLAHI XHEHDE ‘EJMANIHIM LE’IN XHA’EHUM NEDHIRUN LEJEKUNUNNE ‘EHDA MIN ‘IHDAL-’UMEMI FELEMMA XHA’EHUM NEDHIRUN MA ZADEHUM ‘ILLA NUFURÆN
  35,43,ESTIKBARÆN FIL-’ERDI WE MEKRE ES-SEJJI’I WE LA JEHIKUL-MEKRU ES-SEJJI’U ‘ILLA BI’EHLIHI FEHEL JENDHURUNE ‘ILLA SUNNETEL-’EWWELINE FELEN TEXHIDE LISUNNETI ELLAHI TEBDILÆN WE LEN TEXHIDE LISUNNETI ELLAHI TEHWILÆN
  35,44,‘EWELEM JESIRU FIL-’ERDI FEJENDHURU KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETUL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM WE KANU ‘ESHEDDE MINHUM KUWETEN WE MA KANEL-LAHU LIJU’XHIZEHU MIN SHEJ’IN FI ES-SEMAWATI WE LA FIL-’ERDI ‘INNEHU KANE ‘ALIMÆN KADIRÆN
  35,45,WE LEW JU’UAHIDHU ELLAHU EN-NASE BIMA KESEBU MA TEREKE ‘ALA DHEHRIHA MIN DABBETIN WE LEKIN JU’UEHHIRUHUM ‘ILA ‘EXHELIN MUSEMMEN FE’IDHA XHA’E ‘EXHELUHUM FE’INNALL-LLAHE KANE BI’IBADIHI BESIRÆN